Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个一模一样 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家的孩子 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 我们可没空搞这种小噱头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}大总统的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东方之都 东方之都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是斯卡的新情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在到处逃亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够顽强的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我没看前面 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很少见的服装呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从清来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是来观光的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东方之都没什么可看的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是因为换乘顺便逛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（三号站台出发的列车是…）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（开往罗斯城的）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（搭乘这趟列车的乘客请尽快上车）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是只奇怪的猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实听到了脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑发的中年男人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 报告里确实是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边出现了数名轻重伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡也是拚尽全力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太显眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好 和我没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是葬礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不想谈这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这个年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会想起不知什么时候自己也会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在说什么 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来 您还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拉曼中将阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见面地点是在休斯准将的墓前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然使用了最终手段 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一般的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一 男扮女装过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不愧是出名的怪人古拉曼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意外的装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就作为好话接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去中央图书馆的话 也许能知道点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找不到豆丁女的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕能找到一点线索就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央高层全部是一伙的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 和得到的情报相比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失去的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能信赖的部下全部被分散了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是偷鸡不成蚀把米吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 连雷文也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 我还在中央的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被雷文这样问过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“对完全不死的军团有没有兴趣？”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的军团？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不屑一顾地说 不死什么的真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这之后马上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被贬到东方司令部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左迁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个不得不收拾东方那些乱七八糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还记得里奥尔的暴动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷多教假教主的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被钢之炼金术师揭露的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥尔陷入了大混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初期阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东方军迅速行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制了暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 中央军出动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把东方军赶出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥尔的治安急速恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在中央军进驻以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央的家伙们 看来有什么阴谋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我引退之前 就不能平平安安的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您又开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拉曼阁下这样的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是以地方之首就能满足的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您手上明明有经历了伊修瓦尔之战的强力东方军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为机密联络的便条
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只有在向我诉苦的时候才用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是为了煽动我才把我叫来的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为中央变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要熄灭的野心的火种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始燃烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动真格的话 妆会掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 在哪里喝杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 很高兴你能邀请我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于炼丹术的资料为什么那么少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索性去清国学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 用机械铠穿越那个沙漠有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少 少佐 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 在图书馆要安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像在找带着黑白猫的清国少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听马斯坦古大佐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我是替大佐来传话的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少女似乎要去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照目击者的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是从东方之都去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 只要知道这点就能行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也向大佐道声谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 别太急
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许派得上用处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁？见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方司令部的更北方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护着和德拉古马的国境线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着布里克斯北壁之称号的将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯壮少将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡 你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向司令部报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是去西方之都的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到像样的炼丹术资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫梅的孩子用的远程炼成术太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能使用那个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在诺克斯医生那里的时候多打听一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟说是在医学方面特化的技术 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是钢之炼金术师先生的兄弟 高大的铠甲先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 在图书馆要安静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学习什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼丹术？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国的炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清国的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 艾尔利克兄弟是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在炼金技术发达的国家亚美斯多利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得国家资格的能人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在调查别国的下等炼金术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了恢复我的身体什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查能和人造人对抗的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都没法说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 因为听说炼丹术在医学方面特化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为拯救人命的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有新的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在研究这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 不愧是传闻中的艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备一下 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 在图书馆要安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体情况边走边说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整理一下旅馆的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里的小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是铠甲先生的哥哥 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是国家炼金术师的爱德华先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和传闻一样是个小个子的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你 再说一遍试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一遍试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能飞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去海王星玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 和传闻一样说小会非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从杰利姆大人身边离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是杰利姆·布拉德雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统的儿子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该是要去北方的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子一直崇拜着爱德华先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崇 崇拜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆喜欢炼金术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我也要学习炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想是成为像爱德华先生这样的国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崇拜我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 想帮上爸爸的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢金格·布拉德雷大总统吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是怎样一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能忍受普通人会叫苦连天的繁重工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天为国民着想而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统每天很忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还是现役 拚命地干活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪都一把了 明明可以退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始就是专注工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然工作很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是个不懂女人心的木头人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个失礼的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至都打了他的耳光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个的缘故 开始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的约会又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 变成恋爱故事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有时间 来看看你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且听说钢之炼金术师也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在中央司令部刚见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 在图书馆见到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说我们长得不像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这孩子没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们夫妇没能有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以收了亲戚的孩子作了养子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养育成了孝顺父母的温柔孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直只见过您在司令部的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那个…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是印象的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们的家人稍微有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要回去处理公务了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人和儿子都不知道大总统是人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去北方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打听出炼丹术的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上就会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他彻底逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是西部地区的地图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后目击到的地点是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西方之都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之间的某个地方 斯卡和马克消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拐弯的话 速度要降低很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有跳车的可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 跳车后往哪边逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是南方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是 第一次去北方？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在利塞布尔很少积雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:24:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追逐者 被追者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在白色的世界相撞的疯狂与憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾有过的激斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了通向新世界的门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第33话 布里克斯的北壁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.59,0:24:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是用冰做出来的火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我由于不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:11.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:18.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:21.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:29.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:33.93,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:39.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:44.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:50.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:55.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:23:01.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:06.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:12.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:17.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.94,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:29.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
